<P>A SERMON By <HI>Abraham Hellenbroek.</HI> Sometime Mini&s;ter of the Go&s;pel at <HI>Rotterdam.</HI></P>
<Q><BIBL><HI>From CANTICLES Chap. II. Ver. 15.</HI></BIBL>
<P>Take us the Foxes, the little Foxes that &s;poil the Vines: for our Vines have tender Grapes.</P></Q>
<P>Being one of that Rev. Author's printed Di&s;cour&s;es on the <HI>SONG</HI> of <HI>SOLOMON.</HI></P>
<P>Publi&s;hed at <HI>Rotterdam, Anno</HI> 1717. <HI>Tran&s;lated from the Dutch.</HI></P>
